      "acceptanceCriteria": "N≥10 constructs from production lots tested across two independent laboratories; dimensional and material conformance verified.",
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs from production lots were tested across two independent laboratories (FDA CDRH and DePuy Synthes). Each construct was assembled per ASTM F1717 protocol. Dimensional conformance was verified by CMM inspection. Material certificates confirmed Ti-6Al-4V alloy composition. Sample size exceeds the minimum required for this risk level. Achieved level equals required level."
    },
    {
