      "rationale": "Three primary QoIs were evaluated: construct stiffness (E/uval = 0.81, 2.4% difference), yield force (E/uval = 1.12, 3.4% difference), and force at 40 mm displacement (E/uval = 0.67, 2.2% difference). All metrics satisfy both the E/uval < 1.96 and <10% percentage difference acceptance criteria. Output comparison is comprehensive and quantitative. Achieved level equals required level."
